com.netflix.msl.msg
Class MessageCapabilities

java.lang.Object
  com.netflix.msl.msg.MessageCapabilities

public class MessageCapabilities
extends Object

The message capabilities identify the features supported by the message sender.

The message capabilities are represented as capabilities = { "compressionalgos" : [ enum(GZIP|LZW) ], "languages" : [ "string" ], } where:

  • compressionalgos is the set of supported compression algorithms
  • languages is the preferred list of BCP-47 languages in descending order
